<div class="lead-in">
            <p class="lead-in__title" id="the-drying-of-the-earth-accelerated-in-recent-years">The Drying of the Earth Accelerated in Recent Years</p>
                <div class="lead-in__intro">
            <p>The dramatic depletion of groundwater and surface water plus the melting of glaciers between 2014-24 has connected once-separate arid places, forming “mega-drying” regions that stretch across whole continents.</p>

        </div>
    </div>


