        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            We’ve updated our database with the latest financial filings from eight justices, detailing millions in book income, almost 40 trips and one gift.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
                        <span class="story-card__byline-author">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/sergio-hernandez">Sergio Hernández</a>,
            </span>
                        <span class="story-card__byline-dateline">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2025-07-25EDT05:00">July 25, 2025, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
            </span>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
            </div>
            </ol> <!-- end .most-read-group -->

</div> <!-- end .most-read -->

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

    
