                    <li>You can’t sell our material separately or syndicate it. This includes publishing or syndicating our work on platforms or apps such as Apple News, Google News, etc.</li>

                    <li>You can’t republish our material wholesale, or automatically; you need to select stories to be republished individually. (To inquire about syndication or licensing opportunities, contact <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#9df1f4fef8f3eef4f3faddedeff2ede8fff1f4fefcb3f2effa"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="2c40454f49425f45424b6c5c5e435c594e40454f4d02435e4b">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>.)</li>

